WEBVTT

00:01:58.875 --> 00:02:04.058
Twenty-six precious lives were taken
in my carriage alone,

00:02:05.042 --> 00:02:06.970
and I was almost one of them.

00:02:08.855 --> 00:02:11.596
In the time it takes to draw a breath,

00:02:11.620 --> 00:02:15.290
we were plunged into a darkness so immense

00:02:15.314 --> 00:02:17.696
that it was almost tangible;

00:02:17.720 --> 00:02:22.079
what I imagine wading
through tar might be like.

00:02:23.398 --> 00:02:25.448
We didn't know we were the enemy.

